{"parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Campaigns"}], "prev": {"link": "../voice_campaign_performance/", "title": "Voice: Viewing the Performance of a Voice Campaign"}, "next": {"link": "../sent_voice_campaign/", "title": "Voice: Interacting With a Sent Voice Campaign"}, "title": "Voice: Interacting With a Voice Campaign in Draft Mode", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"voice-interacting-with-a-voice-campaign-in-draft-mode\">\n<h1>Voice: Interacting With a Voice Campaign in Draft Mode<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#voice-interacting-with-a-voice-campaign-in-draft-mode\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">Once you have <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/new_voice_campaign.html\">created your voice campaign</a> , it will be in draft mode.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">During this stage, you will have the opportunity to edit and design your <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/voice_campaigns.html\">voice campaign</a> to create a new version before you decide to send it.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">You will need to have navigated to the desired <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/voice_campaigns.html\">voice campaign</a> to follow the steps below.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i> and click <strong>Edit Campaign</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_edit.html\">Edit</a> the fields of your voice campaign</p></li>\n<li><p>When satisfied, click <strong>Save</strong></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i> and click <strong>Send/Schedule Campaign</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>Curate the list of recipients of the voice campaign under <strong>To</strong> (options detailed <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/campaigns/guides/voice/new_voice_campaign.html\">here</a> )</p></li>\n<li><p>You can opt to <strong>Schedule Delivery</strong> instead of the default option to <strong>Send Immediately</strong> by selecting a date and entering a time</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Send</strong></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i> and click <strong>Delete Campaign</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>Click <strong>Yes</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Note that in addition to your voice campaign, all associated workflows will be deleted</p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Design Workflow</strong> to design your voice campaign <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/design_a_workflow.html\">workflow</a> using the blocks below:</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/play_recording_block.html\">Play Recording</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/speak_text_block.html\">Speak Text</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/go_to_menu_block.html\">Goto Menu</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/dial_by_extension_block.html\">Dial by Extension</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/dial_by_name_block.html\">Dial by Name</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/dial_menu_block.html\">Dial Menu</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/forward_call_block.html\">Forward Call</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/voicemail_block.html\">Voicemail</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/if_then_block.html\">If/Then</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/wait_block.html\">Wait</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/set_goal_block.html\">Set Goal</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/set_variable_block.html\">Set Variable</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/time_of_day_block.html\">Time of Day</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_property_block.html\">Update Property</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_consent_block.html\">Update Consent</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_lists_block.html\">Update Lists</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_topics_block.html\">Update Topics</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/enroll_in_a_workflow_block.html\">Enroll in Workflow</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_email_block.html\">Send Email</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_sms_block.html\">Send SMS</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_internal_email_block.html\">Send Internal Email</a> , <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_internal_sms_block.html\">Send Internal SMS</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/campaigns/guides/voice/sent_voice_campaign", "Voice: Interacting With a Sent Voice Campaign", "N", "next"], ["users/campaigns/guides/voice/voice_campaign_performance", "Voice: Viewing the Performance of a Voice Campaign", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/campaigns/guides/voice/draft_mode_voice_campaign.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Voice: Interacting With a Voice Campaign in Draft Mode</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/campaigns/guides/voice/draft_mode_voice_campaign", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}